<category term="Royal台北星期四文章" scheme="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewforum.php?f=3" label="Royal台北星期四文章"/>
<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=728&amp;p=756#p756"><![CDATA[
05/11 (Thu) What are the benefits of dancing?/ 17 Proven Tips to Sleep Better at Night (Host: Joyce)<br /><br /><br />We will hold an on-site meeting only.<br />摩斯漢堡明曜店(每人低消 :60元)<br />台北市仁愛路4段151巷37號地下室.<br />MRT忠孝敦化站3號出口 , 明曜百貨後方第二個巷子口<br /><br />Royal 台北 ( Thursday )<br />**** NEW***     Meeting time agenda:7:00-9:00 PM<br />7:00-7:30  Chatting time with your favorite drink, and introduction of the meeting by the host<br />7:30-8:00  discussion of the first topic<br />8:00-8:05  Take a group photo<br />8:05-8:30  discussion of the second topic<br />8:30-9:00  Individual Presentation (each person will have two minutes to give a presentation on any topic of that day. <br />)<br /><br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><span style="font-weight: bold"><br />Session 1, What are the benefits of dancing?</span><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.openaccessgovernment.org/benefits-of-dancing/127275/#:~:text=Dance%20is%20a%20rhythmical%20form%20of%20exercise%2C%20where,everyday%20life.%20Hence%20dancing%20lowers%20stress%20and%20anxiety">https://www.openaccessgovernment.org/be ... %20anxiety</a><!-- m -->.<br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Do you dance? Why most men won’t dance? Do you think the majority of men have very hard rhythmic timing and they don’t know how to move their bodies?<br />2.What are the pros and cons of dancing?<br />3.Why does your other half hate seeing you social dance with others? How to social dance without losing your partner?<br />4.Do you think most of the time, women are faster natural dancers than men?<br />5.What are the pros and cons of being a dancer?<br /><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Session 2, 17 Proven Tips to Sleep Better at Night!</span><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.healthline.com/nutrition/17-tips-to-sleep-better">https://www.healthline.com/nutrition/17 ... eep-better</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Do you often find yourself unable to get to sleep or regularly waking up night at night? Are you tired of tossing and turning at night?<br />2.Does personality influence sleep patterns?<br />3.How to sleep better?<br />4.Do sleep gadgets and apps help you fall asleep? How can technology help you fall asleep faster?<br />5. Diet, exercise, and sleep are three pillars of a healthy life. How to improve these lifestyle factors to help people lead longer lives?<br /><br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=55735">zoe</a> — Fri May 05, 2023 2:06 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
