02/23 (Thu) Trying to eat well on a budget? Here's a full week of nutritious meals that cost less than $5 a day / China’s young ‘lie flat’ under social challenges (Host: George,  Meeting May)<br />We will hold an on-site meeting only.<br /><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: #800000">摩斯漢堡明曜店</span></span>(每人低消 :60元)<br />台北市仁愛路4段151巷37號地下室.<br />MRT忠孝敦化站3號出口 , 明曜百貨後方第二個巷子口<br /><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Agenda</span><br />7:00-7:30 pm ：opening ＆free talk<br />7:30-8:00 pm: session I, the first topic, subgroup discussion<br />8:00-8:30 pm: session 2, the second topic ,subgroup discussion.<br />8:30-9:00 table topic<br /><br /><br /><br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br /><br />Session I :Trying to eat well on a budget? Here's a full week of nutritious meals that cost less than $5 a day.<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.insider.com/guides/health/diet-nutrition/how-to-eat-healthy-on-a-budget?amp">https://www.insider.com/guides/health/d ... budget?amp</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Question<br />1. Are you trying to eat healthy? Do you spend a lot of money?<br />2.What is your monthly budget for eating? <br />3.Do you do the shopping list when you do grocery shopping?<br />4.Article says that you can decrease the spend for doing meal prep. Have you ever try this before?<br />5.Please share your personal tips for saving money especially on eating budget.<br /><br />----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br /><br />Session II: China’s young ‘lie flat’ under social challenges<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.eastasiaforum.org/2022/10/27/chinas-young-lie-flat-under-social-challenges/">https://www.eastasiaforum.org/2022/10/2 ... hallenges/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Question<br />1.     What is “lie flat”? Have you ever heard this word before?<br />2.Do you “lie flat”? Is it ok to “lie flat”?<br />3.What are the possible reasons that there are many young generations who “lie flat”?<br />4.Is it immoral to “lie flat”, especially in the workplace?<br />5.Since the global economy is getting worse and worse. Do you think that the younger generations will become “lie flat”? Why?<br /><br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=55735">zoe</a> — Tue Feb 21, 2023 8:02 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
