2/16(THU.) ChatGPT &amp;Five Ways Hiking Is Good for You (Host:Shuman, Meeting host:William)<br />We will hold an on-site meeting only.<br />摩斯漢堡明曜店(每人低消 :60元)<br />台北市仁愛路4段151巷37號地下室.<br />MRT忠孝敦化站3號出口 , 明曜百貨後方第二個巷子口<br /><br />Royal 台北 ( Thursday )<br />Agenda,<br />7:00-7:30 pm ：opening ＆free talk<br />7:30-8:00 pm: session I, the first topic, subgroup discussion <br />8:00-8:30 pm: session 2, the second topic ,subgroup discussion.<br />8:30-9:00 table topic<br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Article 1: ChatGPT <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.dailysabah.com/opinion/op-ed/chatgpt-and-i-wrote-this-article">https://www.dailysabah.com/opinion/op-e ... is-article</a><!-- m --><br /><br />(以下補充)<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2N4KouAlJDc">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2N4KouAlJDc</a><!-- m --> (讓火爆全網的ChatGPT寫學測題目 他能拿幾分呢?)<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WizoCwjEKsg">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WizoCwjEKsg</a><!-- m --> (CHATGPT寫論文)<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://businessfocus.io/article/223265/chatgpt-%E7%B7%A8%E7%A8%8B-%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B8%AB?fbclid=IwAR28VOUvVL6iehep7Or_Jo8KmUBo-4JHVdU3KapZJFTS7tzO3ptFRT4HCt0">https://businessfocus.io/article/223265 ... ptFRT4HCt0</a><!-- m -->  (CHATGPT達工程師水準)<br /><br /><br />Question<br />1.How many do you know for ChatGPT?<br />2.Is ChatGPT Safe? Why?<br />3.What kind of job will be replaced by ChatGPT soon?<br />4.Would you like to try download ChatGPT app and use it? <br />5.Free to ask<br />----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Five Ways Hiking Is Good for You<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://greatergood.berkeley.edu/article/item/five_ways_hiking_is_good_for_you">https://greatergood.berkeley.edu/articl ... od_for_you</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Question<br />1.What kind of benefit can we can when we go hiking?<br />2.Fatigue legs is always happened after hiking. How do you train your legs muscle? <br />3.What should we avoid when hiking? How to deal with unexpected cramp?<br />4.What is the more challenging hiking trait you ever done?<br />5.Free to ask<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=872">Shuman</a> — Thu Feb 09, 2023 9:03 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
